{"tid":2395629,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國據報去年驅逐 3 中國間諜　全以新聞工作簽證入境　掩飾公安部情報員身份","createTime":"2021-02-05T04:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T05:26:39.000Z","uid":56115,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4f165d8ef0a39b5186115f311decf9d7f2850c95","tid":2395629,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:23:35.000Z","msg":"英國《每日電訊報》周四指，英國去年驅逐了 3 名以新聞工作簽證入境的中國間諜。<br />\n<br />\n該報道引述英國政府消息來源指，該 3 名中國公安部的情報官員佯稱為 3 家中國媒體機構工作，其真實身份最終被軍情五處 (MI5) 發現，被強制遣返中國。<br />\n<br />\n路透社指，該消息未得到獨立核實。<br />\n<br />\n同樣在周四，英國通訊管理局宣佈吊銷中國環球電視網 (CGTN) 在當地的廣播牌照。 CGTN 是中國官媒中央廣播電視總台旗下的媒體，過去一直被指報道手法成疑，例如多次播放強迫認罪影片等。在 2019 年 CGTN 曾多次報道香港反送中運動，當中 5 則報道被英國通訊管理局裁定內容偏頗。<br />\n<br />\n來源：<br />\nReuters, UK expelled three Chinese spies posing as journalists in past year: The Telegraph, 5 February 2021"},{"pid":"3177d259ab5405dd8dde471c25ebfc81befb0b80","tid":2395629,"uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E9%A9%85%E9%80%90-3-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C-%E5%85%A8%E4%BB%A5%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-%E6%8E%A9%E9%A3%BE%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E9%83%A8%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%93%A1%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A9%2585%25E9%2580%2590-3-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AB%259C-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583-%25E6%258E%25A9%25E9%25A3%25BE%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD%2F&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9ETY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h